HEADWORD: Taproot
<hw>Tap"root`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The root of a plant which penetrates the earth directly downward to
a considerable depth without dividing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

